'''U大道'''（Avenue U）是[[美国|美国]][[纽约市|纽约市]][[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]]的一条重要街道，开始于格雷夫森德（Gravesend）的史迪威大道（Stillwell Avenue），结束于卑尔根海滩（Bergen Beach）的卑尔根大道（Bergen Avenue），沿线经过的街区还有Homecrest、羊头湾（Sheepshead Bay）、海洋公园（Marine Park）和Mill Basin。

==U大道唐人街==
U大道现已成为布鲁克林区的第二个[[布鲁克林华埠|唐人街]]<ref name = BrooklynChinatowns>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2013/06/09/nyregion/new-york-citys-newest-immigrant-enclaves.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|title=A guide to the new immigrant enclaves of New York City|author=Kirk Semple|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2013-06-08|accessdate=2013-06-09|archive-date=2017-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812063711/http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2013/06/09/nyregion/new-york-citys-newest-immigrant-enclaves.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Ellen Freudenheim |title=Brooklyn: A Soup-to-Nuts Guide to Sites, Neighborhoods, and Restaurants |publisher=St. Martin's Griffin |edition=2nd |date=1999| location=New York |page=103 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=6JDcZ794OuwC&pg=PA103&dq=Avenue+U+Chinatown&hl=en&ei=oS31TZySBYb50gHy1qTtDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CC8Q6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=Avenue%20U%20Chinatown&f=false |isbn=9780312204464|accessdate=2013-02-11}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite book|author=Annie Hauck-Lawson and Jonathan Deutsch (eds.) |title=Gastropolis: Food and New York City |publisher=Columbia University |series=Arts and traditions of the table |date=2009 |location=New York |page=136 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=N7yjunQcc-oC&pg=PA136&dq=Q+trains+goes+to+Brooklyn+Avenue+U+Chinatown&hl=en&ei=Y661TpX3D4PV0QH0pMm-BA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CD8Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false |isbn=9780231136532|accessdate=2013-02-11}}</ref>，在康尼岛大道（Coney Island Avenue）和海洋大道（Ocean Avenue）之间，[[华人|华人]]食品市场，面包店，餐馆，美容美甲沙龙、计算机和消费类电子产品经销店的数量迅速增加。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mta.info/nyct/service/qline.htm |title=MTA/New York City Transit Subway Line Information |publisher=Mta.info |date= |accessdate=2013-02-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130208065422/http://www.mta.info/nyct/service/qline.htm |archivedate=2013-02-08 }}</ref> [[紐約地鐵Q線|紐約地鐵Q線]]连接[[曼哈顿华埠|曼哈顿华埠]]的[[坚尼街|坚尼街]]（Canal Street）与布鲁克林U大道唐人街<ref name="#1"/> 第三个唐人街随后出现在布鲁克林南部的本森社区（Bensonhurst）。  

实际上，U大道唐人街是继[[日落公园|日落公园]]的[[布鲁克林华埠|布鲁克林华埠]]之后，曼哈顿的唐人街的第二次扩展。短短16年期间，华人估计增加了14倍<ref>{{cite web|author=Sallie Han and Daniel Young|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/nydn-features/avenue-u-evolves-mein-st-u-s-article-1.767069|title=AVENUE U EVOLVES INTO MEIN ST., U.S.A.|work=[[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]]|date=1997-02-07|accessdate=2013-02-11|archive-date=2017-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711074643/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/nydn-features/avenue-u-evolves-mein-st-u-s-article-1.767069}}</ref>。

U大道有一个名为纽约沃尔玛的中国超市。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kensingtonkitchen.wordpress.com/2011/04/15/new-york-mart-on-avenue-u/ |title=Local Love: New York Mart on Avenue U |publisher=Kensingtonkitchen.wordpress.com |date=2011-04-15 |accessdate=2012-01-11 |archive-date=2013-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016040510/http://kensingtonkitchen.wordpress.com/2011/04/15/new-york-mart-on-avenue-u/ }}</ref> [[华美银行|华美银行]]（East West Bank）目前为U大道唐人街最大的华人金融机构.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eastwestbank.com/English/BL-Brooklyn.asp |title=Branch Locations - Brooklyn |publisher=Eastwestbank.com |date= |accessdate=2013-02-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120908055015/http://eastwestbank.com/English/BL-Brooklyn.asp |archivedate=2012-09-08 |df= }}</ref>

